attachments.title: jonom/jquery-focuspoint
attachments.text: jquery-focuspoint - jQuery plugin for 'responsive cropping'. Dynamically crop images to fill available space without cutting out the image's subject. Great for full-screen images.

attachments.text: There's no denying that the field of visualization has changed over the past several years, from the heady days of Flash to the current era of HTML5 and d3.js. But have we reached Peak Visualization?
